Snippets

To use:
  Drag an .mp3 or .wav file into the browser window.
  Wait for the server to break up your file into a bunch of 1 beat segments.

  [[spinning icon]]

  Click on a square to play it.

  To create a sample, drag a square next to another one. They will snap together.

  To play, click the play icon on each square or collection of squares. Or, put your mouse over a square and
  
  Drag some clips down to the "play" area to create loops.


